{"id":411,"date":"2020-01-07T10:32:18","date_gmt":"2020-01-07T10:32:18","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/sunup.edu.bd\/?page_id=411"},"modified":"2021-09-02T05:42:33","modified_gmt":"2021-09-02T05:42:33","slug":"exam-rules","status":"publish","type":"page","link":"https:\/\/sunup.edu.bd\/exam-rules\/","title":{"rendered":"Exam Rules"},"content":{"rendered":"\n\t<section class=\"section\" id=\"section_1286799191\">\n\t\t<div class=\"bg section-bg fill bg-fill  \" >\n\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\t<div class=\"section-bg-overlay absolute fill\"><\/div>\n\t\t\t\n\n\t\t<\/div>\n\n\t\t<div class=\"section-content relative\">\n\t\t\t\n\n<div class=\"row row-small align-middle align-center\"  id=\"row-749313841\">\n\n\n\t<div id=\"col-152169965\" class=\"col small-12 large-12\"  >\n\t\t<div class=\"col-inner\"  >\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\n\n<div class=\"container section-title-container\" ><h1 class=\"section-title section-title-normal\"><b><\/b><span class=\"section-title-main\" style=\"color:rgb(0, 149, 232);\"><i class=\"icon-star-o\" ><\/i>Exam Rules<\/span><b><\/b><\/h1><\/div>\n\n\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\n<style>\n#col-152169965 > .col-inner {\n  margin: 0px 0px -30px 0px;\n}\n<\/style>\n\t<\/div>\n\n\t\n\n\t<div id=\"col-1902893025\" class=\"col medium-7 small-12 large-8\"  >\n\t\t<div class=\"col-inner\"  >\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\n\n\t<div id=\"text-2184437755\" class=\"text\">\n\t\t\n\n<ul style=\"text-align: justify;\">\n<li>No folder is allowed in the Exam Hall- one board is sufficient to write on.<\/li>\n<li>Students must carry their pen, eraser, sharpener (all is needed to write) in their hands or in a transparent plastic pencil box\/bag.<\/li>\n<li>Students are not to borrow anything from anybody during the examination.<\/li>\n<li>Talking inside the exam hall is forbidden. The student may be asked to leave the room at the teacher\u2019s discretion.<\/li>\n<li>When the examination starts, the student must write his\/her name only on the question paper. No other writing is permitted.<\/li>\n<li>Students must write their name, class and subject on the front page and on alternate pages. Students must also number their pages. They must mark the answer correctly.<\/li>\n<li>An unmarked answer will not be corrected or marked.<\/li>\n<li>The math rough work should be done on the right side of the answer script after drawing a 1.5-inch margin.<\/li>\n<li>Students must not read the question paper before the bell rings to start the exam. The question paper will be placed upside down on their desks during this time. They must not write anything after the bell rings to end the exam.<\/li>\n<li>Any student arriving later than half an hour of the scheduled exam time will not be permitted extra time.<\/li>\n<li>No student may leave the exam hall 15 minutes before the allotted time.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n\t\t\n<style>\n#text-2184437755 {\n  line-height: 1.5;\n  color: rgb(0,0,0);\n}\n<\/style>\n\t<\/div>\n\t\n\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t<\/div>\n\n\t\n\n\t<div id=\"col-782575811\" class=\"col medium-5 small-12 large-4\"  >\n\t\t<div class=\"col-inner\"  >\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\n\n\t<div class=\"img has-hover x md-x lg-x y md-y lg-y\" id=\"image_1433508855\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"img-inner dark\" >\n\t\t\t<img width=\"980\" height=\"1024\" src=\"https:\/\/sunup.edu.bd\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/01\/Sunup-Logo-980x1024.png\" class=\"attachment-large size-large\" alt=\"\" loading=\"lazy\" srcset=\"https:\/\/sunup.edu.bd\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/01\/Sunup-Logo-980x1024.png 980w, https:\/\/sunup.edu.bd\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/01\/Sunup-Logo-287x300.png 287w, https:\/\/sunup.edu.bd\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/01\/Sunup-Logo-768x803.png 768w, https:\/\/sunup.edu.bd\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/01\/Sunup-Logo-1469x1536.png 1469w, https:\/\/sunup.edu.bd\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/01\/Sunup-Logo-1959x2048.png 1959w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 980px) 100vw, 980px\" \/>\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n<style>\n#image_1433508855 {\n  width: 100%;\n}\n<\/style>\n\t<\/div>\n\t\n\n